  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Starting with version 24 RenderMan includes an entirely new diagnostics sub-system, re-written from the ground up to incorporate live, configurable statistics. See RenderMan page </span><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661835\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">here</span></a><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">.</span></p><p>To continue to use the legacy statistics, check <strong>Render Statistics</strong> option in your RenderMan RIS ROP's<strong> Options | Statistics </strong>Tab:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"618\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646109/stats.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433149615&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=618&amp;height=402\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646109/stats.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433149615&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"406\" data-width=\"623\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646125\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"stats.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646109\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ee6624df-5585-40bf-9c3b-d8b365572e59\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646109/stats.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433149615&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=623&amp;height=406 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646109/stats.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433149615&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=618&amp;height=402 1x\"></span><p>By default, it uses the Disk File's path and base name. </p><p>You can view the output xml file with any web browser.  See <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661849\" rel=\"nofollow\">Legacy Diagnostics</a> for more information.</p><p /><ul><li><p><strong>File</strong>: Generate a .stats file </p></li><li><p><strong>XML File</strong>: Generate an XML file for viewing in a browser</p></li><li><p><strong>IO Trace Filename</strong>: A detailed input/output report saved as XML</p></li><li><p><strong>Stylesheet</strong>: The stylesheet used for formatting an XML file</p></li><li><p><strong>Shader Profile</strong>: Profile for custom shader output</p></li><li><p><strong>Displace Ratios</strong>: Suppress reporting of displacement values when divided by the max displacement fall inside this range</p></li><li><p><strong>Maximum Displacement</strong>: The number of warnings for displacement values to print before stopping, 0 means all values reported</p></li><li><p><strong>Enable Texture Statistics</strong>: Allows finer grained reporting of texture usage</p></li><li><p><strong>Track Asset Objects</strong>: Tracks scene entities</p></li></ul>"
    }
  },
